https://github.com/railwayapp/nixpacks # Nixpacks (by Railway)
https://github.com/nlewo/nix2container # converts a Nix package to a Docker container
https://github.com/tazjin/nixery # container registry that converts source code to an image on-demand, using the Nix package manager
https://github.com/reproducible-containers/buildkit-nix # Buildkit - uses a Nix derivation as a Dockerfile
https://github.com/nix-community/nixos-generators # several image builders
https://github.com/the-nix-way/real-world-devops-with-nix # demo - builds containers with Nix and deploys them to Kubernetes on Digital Ocean
https://github.com/fluent-ci-templates/dockerfiles/ # Nix-based Dockerfiles (by Fluent CI)
